			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Hello all.
<br />

<br />
Somewhat n00b bard here, I am learning to kite and doing a pretty good job controlling the area I utilize and the Mobs I am kiting.  I am getting the timing down pretty well. 
<br />

<br />
I was in MS and OT doing ok ... but each time I get adds.  No problem until one of the early Mobs gets to 10% or so and walks away from the pack.
<br />

<br />
Then I don't know what to do.  Is it only certain Mobs that run? Should I avoid those Mobs?  When the one runs, if I chase it, I end up with a bunch of adds.  Not too mention, I don't have weapons equiped at that time.  
<br />

<br />
I could use some help / advice here if you have a sec.
<br />

<br />
Thanks bunches!
<br />

<br />
Roccka
<br />
25 Vah Shir Bard on Bristlebane</span></td>
