				<td colspan="2"><span>Go to Iceclad and hunt Snowcougars.  You can learn to fearkite there too,  just pull the cats down to the shore between the dock and the camp and then snare/fear/fulfill's with Jonathans Whistling Warsong if you can do four songs.  
<br />

<br />
Everyone thinks of Iceclads as an AoE spot but if the cats are warping then fearkiting is nearly as fast and a lot safer.  
<br />

<br />
Another good trick is to charm Midnight and use him to kill the other cats fast,  when his health gets low you can fear him.  
<br />

<br />
I once charmed a frost giant and dragged him back to kill cougars,  that was a lot of fun.</span></td>
