Spent about an hour and a half there last night and got level 31. I took midnight down but did all of it using AoE.  Midnight was a bit harder because he seems to run faster than the other snow cougars.
<br />

<br />
One thing I found out here, as I said the gnolls in Split Paw run so slow that no Sow or Selos is neccessary to keep the correct distance for AoE's. As a matter of fact if you use Selos or SoW you pull too far ahead of the gnolls. With the cougars in IC if I used Selos I pulled away from the cougars.  If I used SoW from a potion bottle, it was just about the right speed. If you don't use either.. you get caught from behind.
<br />

<br />
